      *                                                                                       LUC116
      ** If LUC116 is enabled, and Day No is 36083 (15OCT70). For                             LUC116
      ** Expiry Date (I=2) and/or Last Availability Date (I=11)                               LUC116
      ** Display UFN.                                                                         LUC116
     C           LUC116    IFEQ 'Y'                                                           LUC116
     C           I         ANDEQ2                                                             LUC116
     C           DAY,I     ANDEQ36083                                                         LUC116
     C           LUC116    OREQ 'Y'                                                           LUC116
     C           I         ANDEQ11                                                            LUC116
     C           DAY,I     ANDEQ36083                                                         LUC116
     C                     MOVE 'UFN    ' DAT,I                                               LUC116
     C                     ELSE                                                               LUC116
